Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:12.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried coming alone to our usual park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feeling I've never felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:21.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a child, frightened by the sound of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran back along the path home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:33.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky outside the window is too vast. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, may this reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord, if you ever grant wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:50.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish right now, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:56.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your voice, I miss you! I want to see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you already be looking toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:06.21,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just brush it off, saying the time has slipped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and yet it's been too late since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:19.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give up, it can't be like the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:24.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just decide so simply there's no way, no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.23,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Denton?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:42.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Denton wanted to \Nknow if you were here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:44.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk with us about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes, Professor Denton?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the help of the NIA, I've \Nlooked into a bunch of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we've confirmed we \Nhave a bit of a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a strong response...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they come so far so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Including what happened \Nlast time at the coal mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:04.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the series of incidents \Ncaused by your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Busted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the accident on the \Nisland was not unrelated either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That vine monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey, I bet you've already \Ngot a hunch about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:22.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About the thing that connects \Nall these incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the remnants of the Skrugg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the monsters in the \Ncoal mine resembled the Skrugg,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:36.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but didn't Joey and Heroman \Nalready defeat Kogorr?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Kogorr has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:42.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that explosion didn't \Nwipe out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones that Will is destroying \Nand that I had are examples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what are you going to do, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:04:00.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would be interested in this \Nhyper-technology, not just scientists...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, Will was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:08.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His goal is to destroy \Nthe remnants of the Skrugg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be trying to accomplish \Nsomething by doing that, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow traces of the \NSkrugg to be left on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What you see with your \Neyes is not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have already begun to \Nmove underneath the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Will is not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't like what's coming next, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because crisis is encroaching \Non the world this very second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:17.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to take it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it, and what are they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have firm answers \Nto everything, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only natural to think that the \Nremnants of the Skrugg are trying something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise there'd be no other explanation \Nfor the people kidnapped at the coal mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the Skrugg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:48.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a guess, but I think what went \Non there was some sort of experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:53.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm thinking that the monsters \Nthat showed up were somehow connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, similar incidents \Noccurred all throughout the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly why we must find out the \Ntruth behind what's going on without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, we'll be in real trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show them who the true \Nrulers of this planet are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Skrugg!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take shelter immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an accident in the bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or more accurately, I don't know \Nif it's an accident or something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bunker shouldn't be in operation now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then why did an accident happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The details can wait, sir. First evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you explain yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:52.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:04.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop them, no matter the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll investigate \Nwhat they are trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you figure anything \Nout, please contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The White House has been \Ntaken over by the Skrugg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it was a large scale attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already lost communications \Nwith the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a helicopter ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle may determine the fate of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'd just be holding Joey \Nback if we went with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's something else \Nthat we should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying we should sit on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I 'spose I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much time until we leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,60 minutes. Get ready by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Joey! Where are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a clue, Psy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we should also get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't waver any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina, there's something I have to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.31,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious force that \Ninvaded the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.59,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,are even now still increasing their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:37.55,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received information that all \Ncommunications from the White House have ceased
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.05,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,but there has still been no official \Nstatement from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Why the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only a rumor,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've heard that the bunker under \Nthe White House isn't just a shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's also an unofficial research laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're an independent research organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:05.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so I heard that neither the NIA or even the \NPresident himself know of its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a remnant of the \NSkrugg, as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can get rid of it, there's no \Nway to ensure the President's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.94,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.39,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do you... have a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:07.39,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have something I \Nwant to talk about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:22.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I met my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he met you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:40.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it would be really \Nbad if you found out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that my \Nbrother did something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You see, it was all a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see your \Nface right now, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...definitely protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:08.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:12.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any regrets anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I'm fully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After we get to the airport, we'll take \Na private flight to Washington D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the time we're in the air to \Nlook through all that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:55.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,NIA's tactical team have also come up \Nwith a number of simulations you can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have whatever backup we can provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:05.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything you need, we'll \Nget it immediately. Just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:13.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's one more thing... A \Npresent NIA has prepared for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,NIA developed it at the \Ndirection of Mr. Denton.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.90,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we don't have any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.79,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get me as close to \Nthe center as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? Hold the plane steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower our speed as much as \Nyou can and drop them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, but I can't guarantee anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening rear bay doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A new ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:32.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus power armor that the \NProfessor helped create...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Heroman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one said they could do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go down until we \Ndrop off Joey and Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.45,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:14.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.77,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.15,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point if you and the \Nothers get wrapped up in the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The least we can do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.79,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:26.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Find some open ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,National Airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Head there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Joey, Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their goal... is to resurrect Kogorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:32.40,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get to know you better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:35.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to go at each other with our true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:41.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears and smile are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:46.26,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it is, I won't be scared any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.32,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,With both of us, we can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:54.76,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the one who taught me that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I mutter the words "I was born to meet you"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:07.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,my unease disappears, and my heart burns stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:14.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.30,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:28.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I live feeling the same heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you to the very last,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.68,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the promise built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:40.08,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:45.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We are carving out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:57.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman's battle strength should be increased \Nby the power armor that the Professor developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:24:00.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle that I can't afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The White House, now turned \Ninto a Skrugg base,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:05.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,continues to envelope the \Ncity and grow in size...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The remnants of the Skrugg \Nhave only one goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:11.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To resurrect Kogorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:16.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #24: Resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:18.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman... Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
